moonshot\\\" goal\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 421}, {\"ngram\": \"the inaugural south-eastQueenslandfood summit\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Emma-Kate Rose, the event organiser and director of the Food Connect Foundation, said the target is aimed at addressing a laundry list of systemic issues threatening the reliability of national food distribution system, including increasing extreme weather events which cancut off elongated supply lines.\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 518, \"end\": 522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose\", \"score\": 0.999954286953971, \"rank\": 4.570366528536251e-05, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the event organiser\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 543}, {\"ngram\": \"director\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"the Food Connect Foundation\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 587}, {\"ngram\": \"the target\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"a laundry list\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 642}, {\"ngram\": \"systemic issues\", \"from\": 646, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"the reliability\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"national food distribution system\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 726}, {\"ngram\": \"extreme weather events\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"elongated supply lines\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up to receive Guardian Australia's fortnightly Rural Network email newsletter \\\"Our question is, how do we create a more resilient food system in the long term?\\\"\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 833, \"end\": 851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guardian_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Guardian Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guardian_Australia\", \"dbpedia\